data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom, 2 full bath home located just outside the Village of DeGraff. An asphalt driveway leads to the 2 car attached garage on this 1.5 acre lot. Enjoy views of the rolling farm land and wildlife from the covered front porch.  The master bedroom and laundry room are located on the main floor. The enclosed patio off the master has much potential for a quiet oasis overlooking the fenced-in portion of the yard. Appliances in the kitchen include newly purchased range, dishwasher and overhead microwave. The living room has a pellet stove and open staircase with beautiful wooden railing leading upstairs. Call today for your private showing!
